IcsGUI TMC Installation
-----------------------
To create an installation:
--------------------------
1. cd ~dev/src/ccs_gui/scripts
2. ./icsgui_make_deployment <machine name>
	(suitable machine names:lttmc,ftntmc)
3. Wait for "Deployment ready." message.

To install the IcsGUI onto a TMC machine:
-----------------------------------------
See README.DEPLOYMENT
